{"id": "1003792", "question": "print里的\"%.2f\"是什么意思？", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>print里的\"%.2f\"是什么意思？</p></div>", "viewer": 16723, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>\"%.2f\"显示保留两位小数的浮点数，类似地\"%.3f\"是保留3位小数</p><p>比如</p><pre><code class=\"python\">a = 0.12345\nprint(\"%.3f\"%a)</code></pre><p>打印出来就是0.123</p></div>", "lvl2_answer": ["谢谢回答"]}]}